race.comment: Very even race with a host of these close to a win and just as many first starters. SEALAND (11) was well fancied on debut at Pakenham and ran an eye-catching second. Has upside and drawn well. Expected to feature again. WATTEN ASSETT (5) has been beaten in photos at the last two and freshened since. Bursting to win and looks hard to beat. PARAK (3) is another close to a win. Placed in a richer contest before a break then returned with a nice run when placed again over 1000m. Fitter and with the blinkers added looks a leading player again. SHE'S LOADED (12) was a close-up third fresh then fourth last time over further. Freshened for this and sure to be in the finish. THE REAL MAN (14) is another ready to win. Placed fresh then finished fourth at the latest and drawn for a good run in this.
